pageProduct.name: SUP Fit 30 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Helps fuel your body, ignite thermogenesis and support exercise performance.

FUEL. IGNITE. TRAIN
For times when you want to snooze the alarm or your gym buddy bails, grab a SUP FIT. SUP is your new workout pal that is there to support you and your fitness goals. SUP helps fuel your body, ignite your training and support you exercise performance. 

WHY POP SUP? 
SUP has formulated a supplement to complement your exercise program by helping: 
  • Assist metabolism of nutrients 
  • Maintain focus and mental alertness
  • Support energy production
POPSUP

Size: 30 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Assist metabolism of nutrients
• Maintain focus and mental alertness
• Support energy production
• Helps fuel your body
• Ignites thermogensis
• Supports exercise performance

Warnings

Contains 100mg of caffeine per tablet. Always read the label. Use only as directed. If symptoms persist consult your health professional. Do not use product if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Taken in conjunction with diet and exercise. Store below 25?°C.

Ingredients

Paullinia cupana (Guarana) seed ext. dry conc. std. 302.3mg
- Equiv. to Paullinia cupana seed dry 1060mg
- Equiv. to Caffeine 66.5mg
Camellia sinensis leaf ext. dry conc. std. 5mg
- Equiv. to Camellia sinensis leaf dry 125mg
- Equiv. to Catechins 3mg
Citrus aurantium (Bitter orange) fruit ext. dry conc. std. 75mg
- Equiv. to Citrus aurantium fruit dry 750mg
- Equiv. to Oxedrine 4.5mg
Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12) 400mcg
Panax ginseng (Korean Ginseng) root ext. dry conc. 25mg
- Equiv. to Panax ginseng root dry 250mg
Potassium iodide 65.4mcg
- Equiv. to Iodine 50mcg
Psyllium husk powder 250 mg
Zingiber officinale (Ginger) rhizome ext. dry conc. 13.6mg
- Equiv. to Zingiber officinale rhizome dry 150mg
Pyridoxine hydrochloride (Vitmain B6) 5mg
- Equiv. to Pyridoxine 4.1mg
Chromium picolinate 50mcg
- Equiv. to Chromium 6.2mg
Thiamine hydrochloride (vitamin B1) 230mcg
Riboflavin (Vitamin B2) 210mcg
Caffeine 33 mg
Total caffeine per tablet 100mg

Contains: CONTAINS CAFFEINE

Allergen Contains: Caffeine

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Gluten

Directions

Take 1 film coated tablet daily before meals or exercise to support energy production and exercise performance.
Take 1 film coated tablet, 3 times daily before meals or before exercise to help boost metabolism.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
